---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Ministry Model Canvas" description="A strategic planning framework for churches adapted from the Business Model Canvas">


  <!-- Header Section -->
  <section style="background: white; padding: 3rem 2rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>The Ministry Model Canvas for Churches</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.1rem; color: var(--color-gray); margin-bottom: 0;">Adapted from The Business Model Canvas, the Ministry Model Canvas provides a strategic planning framework specifically designed for churches and ministries.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Canvas Section -->
  <section style="padding: 3rem 2rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="canvas-wrapper">
        <!-- Top Row -->
        <div class="canvas-row-top">
          <!-- Block 2: Connecting Factor -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-2">
            <div class="block-number">2</div>
            <h3>Connecting Factor</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Top 3 connecting factors (e.g. problems, needs, interests)</li>
              <li>What unique, interest-based activities can we offer that align with our ministry's values and the interests of our target audience?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Block 5: Key Activities -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-5">
            <div class="block-number">5</div>
            <h3>Key Activities</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>What are the primary activities required to connect with and serve our target audience effectively?</li>
              <li>Which activities do we need to sustain this model long-term? (e.g. worship services, communication, events, training)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Block 3: Missional Identity -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-3">
            <div class="block-number">3</div>
            <h3>Missional Identity</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>What really is the good news in our context?</li>
              <li>How does our church reflect God's mission in the world?</li>
              <li>What aspects of our ministry are particularly compelling to those in our particular context?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Block 4: Relationships -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-4">
            <div class="block-number">4</div>
            <h3>Relationships</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>What type of relationship do they expect from us? (e.g. community, co-creation, accountability, self-service)</li>
              <li>In what ways can we ensure our relational offerings are accessible and appealing to those new to faith?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <!-- Block 1: Target Audience -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-1">
            <div class="block-number">1</div>
            <h3>Target Audience</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Who is our most important target audience? (demographics, location, time, characteristics)</li>
              <li>Which sub-groups exist? (e.g. families contain parents, kids, youth)</li>
              <li>What role do faith and spirituality play in the target audience's lives?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Middle Row - Resources and Channels -->
        <div class="canvas-row-middle">
          <!-- Block 7: Resources -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-7">
            <div class="block-number">7</div>
            <h3>Resources</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Financial</li>
              <li>Volunteers</li>
              <li>Staff</li>
              <li>Partnerships</li>
              <li>Equipment/Technology/Materials</li>
              <li>Location</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">What existing relationships or networks can we leverage to connect with our target audience?</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Block 6: Channels -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-6">
            <div class="block-number">6</div>
            <h3>Channels</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Where and how will we reach the target audience?</li>
              <li>What relationships do we already have, what relationships do we need to establish? (target audience, city, partner organizations)</li>
              <li>What alternatives exist and are used by our target audience regarding connecting factors?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Bottom Row -->
        <div class="canvas-row-bottom">
          <!-- Block 8: Budget -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-8">
            <div class="block-number">8</div>
            <h3>Budget</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Rent/Facilities</li>
              <li>Salaries</li>
              <li>Utilities</li>
              <li>Communication</li>
              <li>Technology</li>
              <li>Materials & Supplies</li>
              <li>Outreach</li>
            </ul>
            <p style="margin-top: 1rem; font-size: 0.9rem;">What are the costs associated with sustaining our ministry model?</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Block 9: Assessing Missional Effectiveness -->
          <div class="canvas-block block-9">
            <div class="block-number">9</div>
            <h3>Assessing Missional Effectiveness</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>How can we cultivate a posture of prayerful discernment and openness to the Holy Spirit as we assess our church's missional effectiveness?</li>
              <li>How can we design SMART criteria that align with our church's God-given mission?</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Attribution -->
      <div style="margin-top: 3rem; padding: 2rem; background: var(--color-light-gray); border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;">
        <p style="font-size: 0.95rem; color: var(--color-gray); margin: 0;">
          The Ministry Model Canvas is adapted from <a href="https://businessmodelgeneration.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">The Business Model Canvas</a> and is licensed under the Creative Commons Attribution-Share Alike 3.0 Un-ported License. For more information visit <strong>oratio.co</strong>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>


</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .canvas-wrapper {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .canvas-row-top {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.5fr 1.25fr 1.25fr 0.75fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .canvas-row-middle {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .canvas-row-bottom {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .canvas-block {
    background: white;
    border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    position: relative;
    min-height: 200px;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .canvas-block::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, var(--color-blue), transparent);
    opacity: 0.04;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .block-number {
    position: absolute;
    top: -10px;
    right: -10px;
    font-size: 4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: rgba(131, 201, 236, 0.15);
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .canvas-block h3 {
    margin-top: 0;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-dark);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .canvas-block ul {
    list-style: disc;
    margin-left: 1.25rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    line-height: 1.6;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .canvas-block li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .canvas-block p {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--color-gray);
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  /* Responsive adjustments */
  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .canvas-row-top {
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    }

    .block-1 {
      grid-column: 3;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .block-2 {
      grid-column: 1;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .block-3 {
      grid-column: 2;
      grid-row: 1;
    }

    .block-4 {
      grid-column: 1 / 3;
      grid-row: 2;
    }

    .block-5 {
      grid-column: 3;
      grid-row: 2;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .canvas-row-top,
    .canvas-row-middle,
    .canvas-row-bottom {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .block-1,
    .block-2,
    .block-3,
    .block-4,
    .block-5 {
      grid-column: auto !important;
      grid-row: auto !important;
    }

    .canvas-block {
      min-height: 150px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .block-number {
      font-size: 3rem;
    }

    .canvas-block h3 {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .canvas-block ul {
      font-size: 0.85rem;
    }
  }
</style>
